{"tid":1183763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"借今鑒古，我地需否重新審視甚至平反中國歷史書上既漢奸","createTime":"2019-06-03T07:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T07:33:36.000Z","uid":89543,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa3c09020028f461a7d8766e6ab0d562f933520","tid":1183763,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:21:21.000Z","msg":"千百年黎既中華民族統治階層根性根本完全無變過<br />\n而家中國都叫名義上民主<br />\n作為一個共和國政權都可以搞到胡煙瘴氣<br />\n可以推論皇朝時期肯定有過之而無不及（階級差別可以直接屈你機，藉口都唔使搵）<br />\n而家無論香港內地大把人想美軍來了我帶路<br />\n喺歷史書既定義上面呢班人其實全部都係漢奸，更何況歷史係由勝利者寫成，後代可能會將呢班人睇成十惡不赦<br />\n歷史書上面個堆吳三桂、陳公博、汪精衛之流，我地有無必要重新審視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b589e5de7c911b135122998eec54491d15576061","tid":1183763,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63651ccdf9e2a8e17f0d819e6e34d971b22a7283","tid":1183763,"uid":61882,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/222702_46fd4241db63ed04332fb0315cbaeec9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F222702_46fd4241db63ed04332fb0315cbaeec9.png&h=8abbb895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c424dd3560a3d10be29327863ad6281ab75f175b","tid":1183763,"uid":204479,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"63651ccdf9e2a8e17f0d819e6e34d971b22a7283","tid":1183763,"uid":61882,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/222702_46fd4241db63ed04332fb0315cbaeec9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F222702_46fd4241db63ed04332fb0315cbaeec9.png&h=8abbb895&s={S